items.title: Pentagon's Hegseth says US command in 'warrior' Japan being upgraded to deter China
items.description: U.S. Defense Secretary Pete Hegseth described Japan on Sunday as indispensable for tackling Chinese aggression.

items.title: South Korea, China, Japan agree to promote regional trade as Trump tariffs loom
items.description: The countries agreed to "closely cooperate for a comprehensive and high-level" talks on a South Korea-Japan-China free trade agreement deal.

items.title: CK Hutchison will not sign deal to sell strategic Panama ports next week, sources say
items.description: Hong Kong's CK Hutchison will not sign a deal next week to sell its two port operations near the Panama Canal to a BlackRock-led group, Reuters report...

items.title: Trump administration reportedly warns European companies to comply with anti-DEI order
items.description: The Trump administration has reportedly sent letters to European companies asking them to comply with a U.S. executive order banning DEI initiatives.
